title: This Month's GTA+ Membership Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Membership Benefits
subtitle: This Month's GTA+ Membership Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposit directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ members who've signed up for this month (February 16 - March 15) will also receive:

- The new multi-floor Eclipse Blvd Garage
- The Emperor Vectre
- Exclusive Lucha Libre weapon tints for the Knife and Baseball Bat at the Gun Van
- Downtown Cab Co.'s services at no personal cost
- 50% off Acid Lab Supplies
- And more

Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for full details.
